00:38:50,915 --> 00:38:56,480
done in 3D on a large scale with those awful little red and green things back in the 1950s,

623
00:38:56,541 --> 00:38:57,001
I believe.

624
00:38:57,662 --> 00:39:02,166
And what they did is what a whole bunch of people with modern VR are doing, which are

