00:40:40,749 --> 00:40:41,290
master.

650
00:40:43,011 --> 00:40:47,433
You can go from that warm sense of immersion I was showing you.

651
00:40:48,174 --> 00:40:50,937
to really scary horror very quickly.

652
00:40:51,998 --> 00:40:54,961
This is actually, if you have that ability to

